[The Game of Life](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life), also known simply as Life, is a [cellular automaton](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cellular_automaton) devised by the British mathematician [John Horton Conway](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Horton_Conway) in 1970. Image shows a [conus textile](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conus_textile) which shows a cellular automaton pattern on its shell.
